# =============================================================================
# NOTES
# =============================================================================
# 1. Never commit the actual .env file to version control
# 2. Use strong, unique passwords and API keys
# 3. In production, consider using a secrets management system
# 4. Regularly rotate API keys and passwords
# 5. Monitor your API usage to avoid unexpected charges
# 6. Test your configuration with: python -m wholesale_agent.cli.main --config-check